{"tid":83374,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"阿叔偷貓來煮　網民大圍捕","createTime":"2017-01-16T16:17:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-24T17:47:08.000Z","uid":58099,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"395ff46aa1cb6a81099f220ab2f78164a86a793a","tid":83374,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T16:17:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://upload.lsforum.net/users/public/l427754a63.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fupload.lsforum.net%2Fusers%2Fpublic%2Fl427754a63.jpg&h=87656e7a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有市民於指於大埔墟發現有可疑男子鬼祟抱貓上車，對質時又支吾以對，懷疑男子捉走貓隻，拍片放上網求救。<br />\n<br />\n結果網友一呼百應，指出長髮阿叔的住址及工作地點，並認出該貓疑是大埔一燒味店所飼養的貓隻，更聽到有人聲稱「拎返屋企煮」。有熱心網友找上門，最終成功尋得片中主角道歉還貓！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://upload.lsforum.net/users/public/z5352054h63.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fupload.lsforum.net%2Fusers%2Fpublic%2Fz5352054h63.jpg&h=cfdb8576&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▲偷貓叔<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://upload.lsforum.net/users/public/k5194854u63.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fupload.lsforum.net%2Fusers%2Fpublic%2Fk5194854u63.jpg&h=bcee718b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fe8374990cb4cf69023faa6f432bd17bb3d72142","tid":83374,"uid":40662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T16:30:37.000Z","msg":"轉載： <br />\n偷貓賊工作地點喺富善邨 公司名 真會記<br />\n善群樓地下 陳志全議員辦事處 隔離 有間灰色士多房 長毛會出現喺度架"},{"pid":"ee14928e2d73a6130254dfbefc03751a1cb9027c","tid":83374,"uid":66239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T16:35:03.000Z","msg":"天氣凍，煮d野味"},{"pid":"1ca95035096ed9b2b1cdcb0d80d9ff8968ef7b8a","tid":83374,"uid":72173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T16:52:20.000Z","msg":"食貓完全無問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n只係食人地果隻就有問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d59b6268c720023caca11f1cc01b6e09b50ed0c9","tid"